name: Mustang Survival Bluewater 15L Waterproof Roll Top Dry Bag
categories: Bluewater 15L Waterproof Roll Top Dry Bag
description: Reliable waterproofness when on the water or the trail. The cube shape stacks well with other bags and won't roll around in the bottom of your boat.210-denier ripstop nylon with a super-durable TPU coating.Welded construction with tapes seams for reinforcement.Cube design packs together with other cube-shaped bags.Note: these dry bags do not provide submersible waterproof protection or impact protection. For electronics, we recommend hard cases with gasket seals.
